1. MultiphaseInterFoam+VDROP to ensure boundedeness by limiting the diffusion and bouyancy

2. OpenFoam version is v2306. Eigen version is 3.4.0 (If using different Eigen version, when compiling the code, there are some warnings but it will compile and calculate well).

3. This version consider the VDROP breakup, no VDROP coalescence, rising velocity and diffusion source term.

4. In constant/transportProperties, the order of each phase must be water, air, then smaller droplets to larger droplets. (17 droplet size)
